      "id": "1750780452991",
      "question_pmp": "A project manager is using a data analysis technique to determine if sufficient resources are available for an upcoming critical phase of a manufacturing project. The technique involves checking if the current resource allocation aligns with the project schedule and if there are any potential bottlenecks. Which specific data analysis technique is the project manager MOST likely employing?",
