        "OPTION_B": "Initiate immediate hiring for five CRAs, assuming the process will be quick.",
        "OPTION_C": "Update the resource requirements to reflect the scarcity and potentially adjust the project timeline or scope.",
        "OPTION_D": "Outsource the entire clinical research work to a third-party vendor without further analysis."
