        "option_c_result": "CORRECT - Expert judgment involves relying on the knowledge and experience of individuals or groups with specialized education, knowledge, skill, experience, or training. When a project is innovative and lacks historical data or metrics, bringing together 'senior architects, structural engineers, and design specialists' to 'collectively determine' resources is a direct application of expert judgment. This is the most reliable approach in such uncertain environments.",
