        "additional_notes": "This question reinforces the understanding of the key output of the Sequence Activities process. The Project Schedule Network Diagram is the direct result of applying tools and techniques like PDM. It serves as the foundation for all subsequent schedule analyses, including critical path determination. Distinguishing this output from other schedule-related documents like the Gantt chart or schedule baseline is essential for a PMP candidate to demonstrate a clear grasp of the progressive elaboration of the project schedule."
