      "id": "1756633764969",
      "question_pmp": "A project manager is working on a public-sector project to build a new community park. The project team has developed several design options. Before proceeding with a final design, the project manager needs to get feedback from a representative group of community members to gauge their preferences and understand their reaction to the proposed designs. The goal is to get qualitative feedback on specific concepts. What is the most effective tool to achieve this?",
