        "option_b_result": "CORRECT - Mind mapping is an ideal technique for risk identification. It encourages creative, non-linear thinking, allowing the team to generate a wide range of potential risks and visually map out their relationships, which can lead to the discovery of new or interconnected risks that might otherwise be missed. The ability to 'visually group related risks' is a key benefit of this technique.",
