      "question_pmp": "You are a project manager for an engineering firm. A new project to design a custom mechanical part has just been approved. The client is a startup with a fixed budget and a strict deadline. To get a precise and justifiable cost estimate, your team needs to provide detailed estimates for each component's design, material procurement, and manufacturing. Given the project's unique nature and the client's financial constraints, what is the MOST appropriate estimating technique to ensure budget adherence and accuracy?",
