      "question_pmp": "A project manager is developing a schedule for a small web development project. The project has a key resource who is only available for 20 hours per week. The project manager identifies several tasks that would require the resource to work more than their available hours. What is the MOST effective way to resolve this resource over-allocation without extending the project's final deadline?",
