      "question_pmp": "A project manager is developing a schedule and discovers that a key resource, a senior database administrator, is over-allocated and is required to work 60 hours in a single week, while their capacity is 40 hours. There is no float on the critical path. The project manager wants to resolve this issue. What is the MOST appropriate tool or technique to apply?",
