      "id": "1756654640680",
      "question_pmp": "A project manager is analyzing the root cause of a significant delay in the project's software release. The team identified that a key module was not integrated correctly, which led to numerous rework cycles. To visualize the sequence of events and decision points that led to the integration failure, which quality management tool should the project manager utilize to create a clear diagram of the process?",
