        "option_b_result": "CORRECT - A flowchart is a diagram that shows the steps of a process in sequential order, with decision points, loops, and parallel paths. It is the most appropriate tool for visualizing the process that led to the integration failure, allowing the project manager to identify where the process may have gone wrong or where a key step was missed. This is the primary function of a flowchart in quality management.",
