        "additional_notes": "This is a straightforward, easy question that tests the direct definition of a key project document, the Risk Register. The scenario describes the function and content of the document in detail, leaving little room for ambiguity. The distractors are all other valid risk management documents but serve different purposes. The question is a classic PMP-style vocabulary question that tests foundational knowledge.",
