        "additional_notes": "This is a straightforward, easy question that tests the direct definition of a Bidder Conference. The scenario describes the purpose and format of the meeting in detail, leaving no room for ambiguity. The distractors are all other valid procurement tools but serve different purposes. The question tests foundational knowledge and is a good example of a simple 'knowledge recall' question.",
