        "option_c_result": "INCORRECT - Prototypes, especially low-fidelity wireframes and mockups, are not designed to test technical feasibility. This is the purpose of a 'Proof of Concept' or technical testing. The scenario focuses on 'flow' and 'user-friendliness,' which are user experience concerns, not technical ones.",
