        "concepts_to_understand": "Prototypes are a powerful communication and risk mitigation tool. They help bridge the gap between abstract requirements and a tangible product, allowing for early feedback and validation. By engaging stakeholders and users early, the project team can significantly reduce the risk of building a product that does not meet user expectations, which is a leading cause of project failure.",
