        "option_a_result": "INCORRECT - While prototyping is a step toward a clear scope, it does not guarantee a perfect, unambiguous scope baseline. A formal, approved scope baseline is an output of the 'Define Scope' and 'Create WBS' processes, which this action is an input to.",
        "option_b_result": "INCORRECT - A physical model of the exterior does not test the core functionality. This is the purpose of a proof of concept. The scenario is about the physical form factor and user experience.",
