        "option_d_result": "INCORRECT - While prototyping adds an extra step, it is intended to save time and cost in the long run by preventing costly rework and scope changes later in the project. The statement that it will 'significantly extend' the timeline is not a likely outcome and misrepresents the value of this tool.",
