        "OPTION_B": "The team is in the 'Goal Clarification' stage; the project manager's objective is to facilitate a shared understanding of the goals.",
        "OPTION_C": "The team is in the 'Commitment' stage; the project manager's objective is to get buy-in from all team members.",
        "OPTION_D": "The team is in the 'High Performance' stage; the project manager's objective is to maintain momentum and celebrate wins."
