      "id": "1756657972902",
      "question_pmp": "The project manager for a new product launch has discovered that the initial project plan is no longer aligned with the company's strategic goals. The company's new strategy is to focus on a high-end, premium market, while the project plan is still focused on a mass-market, low-cost product. The project manager needs to revise the project's scope to align with the new strategy. What is the MOST appropriate process for the project manager to undertake to ensure the project meets the new strategic objectives?",
