      "id": "1756657981983",
      "question_pmp": "The Scrum team is in the middle of a sprint, and the product owner is working with the team to prepare for the upcoming sprints. The product owner is reviewing the product backlog to ensure that the user stories for the next few sprints are clear, well-defined, and ready for development. The team is also adding details, estimating the effort, and ensuring the stories are aligned with the product goal. What is this agile activity called?",
