        "option_c_result": "CORRECT - The activity described in the scenario is 'Backlog Refinement,' also known as backlog grooming. It is the ongoing process of adding details, estimates, and order to product backlog items. It ensures that the items at the top of the backlog are ready to be moved into a sprint during sprint planning. The scenario's description of 'preparing for the upcoming sprints' and 'adding details, estimating the effort' is a direct definition of this activity.",
        "option_d_result": "INCORRECT - The 'Daily Scrum' is a short, daily meeting for the development team to synchronize their work and plan for the next 24 hours. It is not an activity for preparing future user stories.",
