        "additional_notes": "This question tests the foundational knowledge of a key agile practice. The scenario's description of 'preparing for the upcoming sprints' and 'adding details, estimating the effort' is a direct definition of backlog refinement. The incorrect options are all other Scrum events, but they are performed at a different time or for a different purpose. This question requires a precise understanding of the different Scrum activities.",
