      "id": "1756660566877",
      "question_pmp": "A project manager is leading an agile team that is building a new financial application. The product owner and stakeholders have identified several high-value features that would create a significant competitive advantage. However, the team has identified that one of these high-value features, 'Dynamic Data Aggregation,' has a high technical risk. The team is concerned that if they build it, it will require a lot of rework and could derail the project. How should the team use a Risk-Adjusted Backlog to address this issue?",
