        "option_d_result": "CORRECT - A project roadmap is the most effective tool. It is a high-level, time-based visual that focuses on key milestones and deliverables, making it ideal for external communication with vendors who only need to know when their services are required without seeing the internal complexities of the project plan.",
        "process_group": "Planning",
