      "question_pmp": "A project manager is about to start a new project for a company that has recently adopted a Project Management Office (PMO). The PMO has created a standardized set of documents for all projects. The project manager needs to create a project charter, a scope statement, and a risk register. What should the project manager use to ensure consistency and efficiency in creating these documents?",
