      "question_pmp": "A project manager is reviewing a cost estimate submitted by the internal project team. The estimate is significantly higher than the initial budget. The project manager is concerned about the accuracy of the team's estimate and needs a way to validate it. What is the MOST appropriate tool or technique for the project manager to use to gain an unbiased, objective assessment?",
